window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>My life is built on secrets. I thought I knew them all.</b></p> <p>When Bruno rides up on a Harley, all muscled and tattooed, it isn’t just the bike that purrs. I’m drawn to the wolf shifter in a way that can’t be denied. </p> <p>But when he can’t take his eyes off me, it’s not for the reason I’d hoped. </p> <p>He knows more about me than I do. </p> <p>My past isn't what I thought it was. My enemies are much more powerful than I’d ever imagined. </p> <p>My destiny alone remains the same. I’ll do whatever it takes to secure the future of werewolves....</p> <p>The Rocky Mountain Pack series is a gritty, sexy, and action-packed paranormal shifter romance.</p> <p><i>Wolf Lies</i> is a full-length novel recommended for mature listeners due to language, sexual situations, and graphic fighting scenes.</p>"; 
